Klopp: &quot;At the end, this is the first XI and a strong bench &ndash; that&rsquo;s what you need when you have a lot of competition and a difficult game.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;We have to mix up the quality with tactical discipline and big heart and desire, greed, aggressiveness&hellip; let&rsquo;s play football.&rdquo;

Klopp: &ldquo;The job of all six in front of the four - we play pretty flexibly offensively so you need to go the short way back in defence.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;That&rsquo;s not about the position, it&rsquo;s about space. It&rsquo;s not only these two. Phil is also good in this, good in tactical things.&quot;
